英国奖2025年：Charli XCX名为年度歌曲作者https://www.nme.com/news/music/music/brit-awards-2025-charli-xcx-named-songwriter-songwriter-s-the-tle-3841320？ XCX为年度的词曲作者Surej SinghWed, 26 Feb 2025 02:08:30 +0000 Music NewsNewsBRIT AwardsBritsDanceElectronicPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3841320 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>查理（Charli）在本周的仪式上也将获得五项奖项</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-charli-xcx-named-songwriter-of-the-year-3841320">Brit奖2025年：Charli XCX名为“年度最佳歌曲作者”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>被评为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025年Brit Awards</a>年度词曲作者奖的获得者 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">这是2025年英国奖的所有提名人</a></strong></li></ul><p>在即将举行的颁奖典礼之前，该颁奖典礼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/date-revealed-for-the-brit-awards-2025-3794739">将于3月1日星期六在伦敦的O2举行</a>，并专门在ITV1和ITVX上播出，英国人宣布Charli将获得年度最佳词曲作者的荣誉。</p><p>她的冠冕是在她的长期合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-g-cook">AG Cook</a> （也与她合作的“小子”）合作之后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-announce-2025-producer-of-the-year-winner-3841036">，被任命为今年的年度制片人</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3825379" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825379" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825379" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825379" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX。学分：吉尔伯特·弗洛雷斯（Gilbert Flores）/通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>2025年英国委员会主席Damian Christian在一份新闻声明中说，Charli XCX的胜利：“ Charli经历了不可否认的一年，将她的Electronic和Pop实验品牌从地下狂欢带到了主流文化的中心。查理（Charli）的歌曲创作是独特的，大胆的，无情的创新性，而且多年来一直是英国领先的词曲作者之一，他的全球现象小子将她的工艺带入了新的高度。我很高兴她因获得当之无愧的奖项而获得认可。”</p><p>查理（Charli）将于本周末以其最高候选人的身份进入英国奖，并以五个点头领先，包括年度艺术家，流行音乐和舞蹈表演。她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">Guess”</a>合作也将参加年度最佳歌曲，而MasterCard则与她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">“ Brat”</a>唱片一起入围了MasterCard年度专辑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">Charli XCX  - “ Brat，它完全不同，但仍然是Brat”评论：俱乐部音乐策展人艺术的杰作</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年也提名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">CURE</a> ，他们因<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">“失落的世界的歌曲”</a>获得了三十年来获得第一个英国人提名 - 他们将获得年度专辑，年度最佳专辑和Alt/Rock Act。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫乐队</a>还与万事达卡（MasterCard）一起被提名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">“当时”</a>的万事达卡（MasterCard） -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">您可以在此处查看2025年英国人奖的完整列表</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3837510" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837510" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837510" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Charli-XCX-performing-copy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837510" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX在2025年2月2日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的Crypto.com竞技场举行的第67届格莱美颁奖典礼上。 （Christopher Polk/Billboard通过Getty Images摄影）</figcaption></figure><p>将于今年表演的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-sam-fender-and-lola-young-announced-as-final-performers-3838761">Sam Fender和Lola Young，他们最近被宣布为最后的现场表演者</a>，并加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-sabrina-carpenter-confirmed-to-perform-3836811">先前确认的表演，例如Sabrina Carpenter</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-first-performers-revealed-3833403">Jade，Shaboozey，Teddy Swim，Teddy Swim，最后的晚餐聚会和Myles Smith</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-name-2025-rising-star-winner-3819335">后者赢得了。今年的新星奖</a>。</p><p> Carpenter将在今年的仪式上获得享有盛誉的全球成功奖。她将加入一个被授予独家奖项的行为精英名册 - 过去的获奖者仅限于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">一个方向</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔（Adele）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">萨姆·史密斯（Sam Smith</a> ）。</p><p>早在11月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-brit-award-trophy-design-for-2025-revealed-3814651">在2025年颁奖典礼之前就揭露了新的奖杯设计</a>。它是由著名的不列颠尼日利亚多学科艺术家加布里埃尔·摩西（Gabriel Moses）创建的，他多年来一直与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> ，Burberry等人合作。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-charli-xcx-named-songwriter-of-the-year-3841320">Brit奖2025年：Charli XCX名为“年度最佳歌曲作者”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
